  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Platelet-rich plasma (PRP) may promote the endometrial growth and improve pregnancy outcome
      of patients with thin endometrium undergoing ART treatments.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
